        public CoreVersion getRequiredCoreVersion()
        Description copied from class: Plugin

        Also this method might return null if no core version is required.

        public java.lang.Class<? extends java.lang.Enum<? extends PluginInternalLanguageEnumContainer>> getInternalLanguageContainer()
        Description copied from class: Plugin
        Returns the internal language enum container of this Plugin, or null if not implemented.

        The items of the given container will be loaded from the .lang resources that should be found at the given resources package. Plugin.getInternalLanguageResourcesPackage().

      • setUpConfig

        protected boolean setUpConfig()
        Description copied from class: Plugin
        This method should setups the configuration.

        Also this should return true if the configuration was loaded successfully, and false if not.

        Note that if this methods returns false, then the plugin will be disabled automatically.
